> My Chinese dream: Judicial fairness. Give back the life of my son.

While China’s new leader Xi Jinping likes to talk about his “Chinese dream”, a
group of Chinese petitioners are using the microblogging site Sina Weibo to
talk about their Chinese dreams. Rachel Lu from Tea Leaf Nation [has
collected](http://www.tealeafnation.com/2013/03/chinese-petitioners-heres-my-
chinese-dream) posts and photos of their dreams.

